Citation.sAbstract: The relative permittivities (er) of carbon dioxide (CO2) + ethanol mixtures (0.050, 0.100, 0.152, and 0.212 mass fractions of ethanol) were measured at (303 to 333) K in the pressure range (7.2 to 30.8) MPa using a direct capacitance method.
Citation.sTitle: Relative Permittivity Measurements of Carbon Dioxide + Ethanol Mixtures
